Package ch.colabproject.colab.api.model.link

Class StickyNoteLink

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.colabproject.colab.api.model.link.StickyNoteLink
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ColabEntity, WithPermission, WithTrackingData, WithWebsocketChannels, ch.colabproject.colab.generator.model.interfaces.WithId, ch.colabproject.colab.generator.model.interfaces.WithJsonDiscriminator, Serializable
    @Entity
public class StickyNoteLink
extends Object
implements ColabEntity, WithWebsocketChannels
    Link to make an information accessible within a card.

    The source of information can be either

    • a card
    • a card content
    • a resource
    • a document
    Author:
    sandra
